{title: Baba yetu}
{key: Bb}

{start_of_verse: 1}
Ky-ri-e, Ky-ri-e e-lei-son.
Ky-ri-e, Ky-ri-e e-lei-son.
Ky-ri-e, Ky-ri-e e-le-i-son.
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: 2}
D g U
b b Ăş ĂŹ ĂŹ Ăş ĂŹ ĂŹ Ăş ĂŹ ĂŹ ĂŹ ĂŹ w & Ky - ri-e, Ky - ri-e e - lei - son.
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: 3}
D g U b b Ăş ĂŹ Ăş ĂŹ ĂŹ ĂŹJ ĂŹJ Ăş w . . & Ky - ri -ĂŹe, Ky - ri - e e - le - Ăşi - son.
